{
  "stem": "16792.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 353.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we register, we write up what we, you know, what we do.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There is that, all kind of stuff, and they give us ruble to buy suits or something to give us.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they make a date.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We didn't understand-- when we fill up the application, we didn't understand what we fill up.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But this is no problem, and they-- they give us a date to be on the-- on the railroad station.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we came to this railroad station, and they put us in-- in-- in-- in big, big wagons.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You know, the open wagons.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Not open, but the cattle wagons.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They put 40 people to a wagon.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "When you go in, it's a door.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It's one side 20, and the other side 20.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And-- and they put two floor-- like a two-- two floor.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "One floor this, up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[SIGHS] And they have got in this particular train, the whole train, was a lot of people.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They've got a special kitchen.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "One-- one train was a kitchen, and one train was a medicine or medical.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And that's all that it was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "No bathrooms, nothing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "No water, no bathroom, nothing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But they did have a day in the morning, they give us instead of 400 gram bread, which supposed to give us, they give us 200, because 200 you want to sell it to somebody else.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And-- and they give us a soup, but the soup was water with something inside, and that's all that they give us.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And they stopped twice a day to relieve ourselves.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "You relief yourself in the sides, whatever it is, and for eat, for food, this particular soup and bread.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "One time they give us 200 gram bread a day, that's all.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
